  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink51-kilavi">vāyil peṟṟup pukuntupōyp puṟattoḻukkam oḻukip piṉpum vāyil vēṇṭum
          talaimakaṟkut tōḻi maṟuttatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink51">
          <l>nīruṟai kōḻi nīlac cēval</l>
          <l>kūrukirp pēṭai vayāa mūra</l>
          <l>puḷiṅkāy vēṭkait taṉṟuniṉ</l>
          <l>malarnta mārpivaḷ vayāa nōykkē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">


          <l> O man from a village!</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where the sharp-clawed hen </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> craves the blue water cock. </l>
          <l> Unripe tamarind is not what she wants</l>
          <l> for the pain [caused by] her cravings for your </l>
          <l> broad chest.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
